{
  "$schema": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Metta-AI/coworld/main/src/coworld/coworld_manifest_schema.json",
  "game": {
    "name": "coworld-tribal-village",
    "description": "A 48-agent Tribal Village Coworld where each player controls one village agent gathering, crafting, fighting tumors, and supporting its team.",
    "owner": "info@metta.ai",
    "runnable": {
      "type": "game",
      "image": "{{TRIBAL_VILLAGE_IMAGE}}",
      "run": ["python", "-m", "tribal_village_env.coworld.server"]
    },
    "config_schema": {
      "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["tokens", "players", "max_steps", "tick_rate"],
      "properties": {
        "tokens": {
          "description": "One connection token per Tribal Village agent slot.",
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 48,
          "maxItems": 48,
          "items": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}
        },
        "players": {
          "description": "One player display-name object per agent slot.",
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 48,
          "maxItems": 48,
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": {
              "name": {"type": "string", "minLength": 1}
            }
          }
        },
        "max_steps": {
          "description": "Maximum simulation steps before truncation.",
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 1,
          "maximum": 10000
        },
        "tick_rate": {
          "description": "Simulation steps per second.",
          "type": "number",
          "exclusiveMinimum": 0,
          "maximum": 60
        },
        "player_connect_timeout_seconds": {
          "description": "Seconds to wait for players before starting with no-op actions for missing slots.",
          "type": "number",
          "minimum": 0,
          "default": 10
        },
        "render_scale": {
          "description": "Integer scale for RGB browser frames.",
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 1,
          "maximum": 4,
          "default": 1
        },
        "window_radius": {
          "description": "Rendered tile radius around each agent for player view windows.",
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 1,
          "maximum": 16,
          "default": 5
        },
        "seed": {
          "description": "Deterministic episode seed used for map generation, replay, and bundled scripted AI mirrors.",
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 1,
          "default": 1
        }
      }
    },
    "results_schema": {
      "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": ["scores", "team_scores", "ticks", "truncation_reason"],
      "properties": {
        "scores": {
          "description": "One cumulative reward score per agent slot.",
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 48,
          "maxItems": 48,
          "items": {"type": "number"}
        },
        "team_scores": {
          "description": "Eight team scores, each summing the six agent scores for that village.",
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 8,
          "maxItems": 8,
          "items": {"type": "number"}
        },
        "ticks": {
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 0
        },
        "truncation_reason": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    },
    "protocols": {
      "player": {
        "type": "uri",
        "value": "https://github.com/Metta-AI/coworld-tribal-village/blob/main/tribal_village_env/coworld/docs/player_protocol_spec.md"
      },
      "global": {
        "type": "uri",
        "value": "https://github.com/Metta-AI/coworld-tribal-village/blob/main/tribal_village_env/coworld/docs/global_protocol_spec.md"
      }
    },
    "docs": {
      "pages": [
        {
          "id": "rules.md",
          "title": "rules.md",
          "content": {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "# Tribal Village Rules\n\nTribal Village has 48 player slots. Each slot controls one agent in an eight-team village, with six agents per team. Agents gather ore, water, wheat, and wood; craft batteries, spears, lanterns, armor, and bread; fight hostile tumors; and support their team's survival. Each player receives a rendered RGB view window and sends one discrete action per tick. The bundled default player runs the existing Nim role-based scripted AI in a deterministic local mirror and still sends actions through the `/player` route. Final scores are cumulative per-agent rewards, with team scores computed by summing each team's six agents."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "play_tribal_village.md",
          "title": "play_tribal_village.md",
          "content": {
            "type": "text",
            "value": "# Play Tribal Village\n\nRun a local episode with `coworld play coworld_manifest.json` or a headless smoke with `coworld run-episode coworld_manifest.json`. Open `/client/global` to watch the map, `/client/player?slot=0&token=...` to inspect or control a slot, and `/client/replay` to view saved replay action logs. Player containers should connect to the exact `COWORLD_PLAYER_WS_URL` supplied by the runner and send JSON actions shaped as `{ \"type\": \"action\", \"action\": 0 }`. The packaged `default-ai-agent` player uses the same image and WebSocket route as tournament players."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "player": [
    {
      "id": "default-ai-agent",
      "name": "Default Scripted AI",
      "type": "player",
      "image": "{{TRIBAL_VILLAGE_IMAGE}}",
      "run": ["python", "-m", "tribal_village_env.coworld.player"],
      "description": "Bundled player that runs the existing Nim role-based scripted AI through the Coworld player WebSocket."
    }
  ],
